I finally got the sought after 4 5 6!!!! My first PB was a 6:10 on July 28th, 2017. So happy this means I achieved such a time in under 1 year! I'm really happy I never gave up on my goals and reached this. Only thing bittersweet though is that OBS stopped recording the game audio during the run so sadly there is no audio available of this run until I finally plug in my microphone after the run finished. This session was meant to just be a practice session only recorded in case something happened and it did! Sorry for the rambling but I figured i should for something like this

Thank you to the SMB1 Speedrunning community and my twitch viewers for such amazing support and believing in me to get a 4 5 6!
